title: Asian Stocks Rise, Treasuries Fall After Jobs Data: Markets Wrap
description: Asian equities advanced for a fifth day, stretching their lead over US peers this year as relatively cheap valuations and firmer growth prospects lured buyers. Treasuries extended their losses after stronger US jobs data.
